        <p MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">To receive a notification from Pulse, you must be subscribed to the feed where the status update was posted (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Pulse/Moderation/Subscribing_to_Topics.htm">Subscribing to Communities and Topics</MadCap:xref>). You must also enable the appropriate Pulse feature in the Notifications tab on the Settings page of your profile (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Pulse/Getting_Started/Creating_and_Editing_Profiles.htm">Editing Your&#160;Profile</MadCap:xref>).</p>
